rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸香港身分證嘅唔係香港人?</blockquote><br />\n咁支那仔住夠7年仲講緊外語果d你又當佢地自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n習總拎美國護照，係美國人？"},{"pid":"ac2aa6599d10de6c564e4db1e3e95c08b7a161c8","tid":488382,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"外傭都係垃圾，惹埋d南亞狗"},{"pid":"b5b70c9e03e65299e391a0201edf6e56fc66af41","tid":488382,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今次放火條友有香港身分證架喎&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n咁佢係咪啡皮狗？<br />\n重點唔係佢有冇身分證<br />\n係啡皮狗擾亂香港秩序</blockquote><br />\n咁份報紙就唔好講咩假難民, 索性直接話<span style=\"color: red;\">南亞裔<del>香港人</del></span>有問題啦.</blockquote><br />\n咁講比較準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸香港身分證嘅唔係香港人?</blockquote><br />\n咁支那仔住夠7年仲講緊外語果d你又當佢地自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔當佢係自己人係一回事, 佢法律上係香港人又係另一回事. 係咪你唔當佢係香港人, 佢就唔係香港人? 我唔當林鄭係香港人, 係咪就可以話佢冇資格做特首?"},{"pid":"02a29feeb960fbdcb51cbe5212d5daf348c40491","tid":488382,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:28:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}